OL,3,CHow a little bowling club under threat
OL,4,Cof closure became national award
OL,5,Cwinners
OL,7,FITV News' Claire Manning went to meet
OL,8,Fmembers when they were nominated for
OL,9,Fthe award
OL,11,FA bowls club that was on the brink of
OL,12,Fclosure has not only survived the last
OL,13,Fyear but thrived - and now been
OL,14,Fcrowned best in the country.
OL,16,FIlfracombe Bowling Club has been named
OL,17,FClub of the Year by Bowls England.
