OL,3,CHow a little bowling club under threat
OL,4,Cof closure became national award
OL,5,Cwinners
OL,7,FClub member Stephen Humphreyson said:
OL,8,F"We're all delighted, there were
OL,9,Fconstant messages back and forth
OL,10,Fbetween members and those at the event
OL,11,Fwanting to know what the result was.
OL,13,F"It means a lot to us because we were
OL,14,Fstruggling at one time, now we've got
OL,15,Fmore members, more players for
OL,16,Fmatches, we're having a good time now."
OL,18,FAfter losing several key players, the
OL,19,Fclub had fewer members and was facing
OL,20,Ffinancial challenges.
