OL,3,CHow a little bowling club under threat
OL,4,Cof closure became national award
OL,5,Cwinners
OL,7,FMr Humphreyson said: "It was hard
OL,8,Fwork, you would struggle to get
OL,9,Fplayers for matches, we were borrowing
OL,10,Fplayers from other clubs.
OL,12,F"We had two new members who had
OL,13,Fdifferent ideas and it changed the
OL,14,Fclub completely."
OL,16,FBowls England says the turnaround is a
OL,17,Ftestament to the remarkable efforts of
OL,18,Findividuals like Neil Mugleston, the
OL,19,Fclub captain, and Barry Gifford, the
OL,20,Fclub president
