OL,3,CHow a little bowling club under threat
OL,4,Cof closure became national award
OL,5,Cwinners
OL,7,FThe club is now a vibrant community
OL,8,Fhub with 83 playing members and a
OL,9,Ftarget of 100 in the next few months.
OL,11,FThey managed to bridge the
OL,12,Fgenerational gap, shifting the average
OL,13,Fage from mid-60s to mid-40s, with an
OL,14,Fequal mix of genders.
