OL,3,CHow a little bowling club under threat
OL,4,Cof closure became national award
OL,5,Cwinners
OL,7,FMr Humphreyson, said: "I think bowls
OL,8,Fis on the up, the problem is people
OL,9,Fthink it's for older people, but
OL,10,Freally it's not, you get a lot of
OL,11,Fyoung players playing, we've got some
OL,12,Fyounger members who've joined who are
OL,13,Funder 20."
OL,15,FThe club's introduction of various
OL,16,Fplaying sessions, morning to evening,
OL,17,Fhelped retain outdoor members through
OL,18,Fthe winter, doubling membership income.
